headline: TD Cowen cuts Domino’s to Hold on delivery and low-income consumer pressures
summary: Investing.com -- TD Cowen downgraded Domino’s Pizza to Hold in a note Monday, warning that ongoing weakness in the pizza delivery category and pressure on lower-income consumers may limit the stock’s upside in 2026.
